what to do first: Starter “Good First Issues”
Issue #1 – Booth / Shop UI

Goal: Create the booth selling system (fictional gadgets).
Tasks:

Add a Booth model with an interact prompt.

Make a BoothGui (item name, price, buy button).

Script server event BoothSold.

Log sale → player’s wallet.
Location: src/BoothSystem/BoothServer.lua

Issue #2 – NPC Alert System

Goal: Alert patrol NPCs when a sale happens.
Tasks:

Listen for BoothSold event.

Add alert animation or lights on nearby NPCs.

Chance of “OfficerCheck” based on sale value.
Location: src/NPCSystem/AlertHandler.lua

Issue #3 – Mobster Auto-Collector

Goal: Add an NPC employee who collects cash automatically.
Tasks:

Create Mobster module with pay interval and cut percentage.

Simple UI to hire/fire mobsters.
Location: src/MobsterSystem/Mobster.lua
